OL,7,FThe family of four had been unwell for
OL,8,Ftwo weeks before the infected water
OL,9,Fbecame public knowledge. Lisa's son
OL,10,Fended up needing hospital treatment
OL,11,Fand later tested positive for
OL,12,Fcryptosporidiosis.
OL,14,FLisa said: "(My first reaction) was
OL,15,Fshock that this could happen.
OL,17,F"We pay a lot for our clean water, and
OL,18,Ffor this to happen in little Hillhead
OL,19,Fwas unbelievable.
