OL,7,F"And then anger, because we were told
OL,8,Four water was safe the day before and
OL,9,Fwe were still drinking it, and that's
OL,10,Fwhat was making us ill.
OL,12,F"They've told us they need three
OL,13,Fconsecutive days of the readings being
OL,14,Fzero. Hillhead reservoir has had about
OL,15,Ffive or six zero days. But yesterday
OL,16,Fit read that there were traces again
OL,17,Fof crypto. Which is worrying.
OL,19,F"We don't feel like we can trust South
OL,20,FWest Water now."
